    <item>
      <title>欧洲领导人下周在巴黎见面，讨论乌克兰</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/european-leaders-to-meet-in-paris-next-week-to-discuss-ukraine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据熟悉计划的人们说，欧洲国家的领导人将于下周在巴黎开会，讨论他们在乌克兰的立场，并要求对和平进程的要求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/european-leaders-to-meet-in-paris-next-week-to-discuss-ukraine</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Mar 2025 18:32:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>西班牙总理桑切斯下个月在中国见XI</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/spanish-prime-minister-sanchez-to-meet-xi-in-china-next-month</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士说，西班牙总理佩德罗·桑切斯（Pedro Sanchez）将于下个月前往中国与习近平总统会面。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/spanish-prime-minister-sanchez-to-meet-xi-in-china-next-month</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Mar 2025 17:46:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波斯尼亚随着塞族分裂演讲的忧虑而攀升欧盟议程</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/bosnia-climbs-up-eu-agenda-as-serb-secession-talk-stokes-worry</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波斯尼亚 - 黑塞哥维那在欧盟峰会上被添加到议程中，因为领导人的警报持续了警告，该领导人的潜在瓦解巴尔干国家可能会释放东南欧的动荡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/bosnia-climbs-up-eu-agenda-as-serb-secession-talk-stokes-worry</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Mar 2025 16:14:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Zelenskiy说，向美国投资核电站</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/zelenskiy-says-open-to-us-investing-in-ukraine-s-nuclear-plants</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Volodymyr Zelenskiy排除了对乌克兰核电站的控制权，但在与唐纳德·特朗普的电话打来电话后，释放了美国对他们进行投资的可能性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/zelenskiy-says-open-to-us-investing-in-ukraine-s-nuclear-plants</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Mar 2025 16:07:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国和意大利摊位欧盟推动向基辅运送弹药</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/france-and-italy-stall-eu-push-to-commit-ammunition-for-ukraine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲外交官说，欧盟领导人为获得50亿欧元（54亿美元）的努力，以确保法国和意大利今年为乌克兰提供弹药，这是欧洲外交官的另一个迹象，这是Bloc面孔取代美国对基辅支持的挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/france-and-italy-stall-eu-push-to-commit-ammunition-for-ukraine</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Mar 2025 14:41:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>土耳其说，我们已经扩大了其俄罗斯气体制裁豁免</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/turkey-says-it-gets-us-sanction-waiver-extension-for-russian-gas</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据一位对此事直接了解的土耳其官员说，美国已同意扩大制裁豁免，这将使土耳其能够继续购买俄罗斯天然气。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/turkey-says-it-gets-us-sanction-waiver-extension-for-russian-gas</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Mar 2025 10:19:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大与贸易战嘎嘎作响的经济选举</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/carney-set-to-call-canada-snap-election-for-april-28-globe-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大总理马克·卡尼（Mark Carney）将在几天之内召集全国大选，在该国与美国的贸易战动摇的时候，寻求自己的授权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/carney-set-to-call-canada-snap-election-for-april-28-globe-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Mar 2025 09:59:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普说，美联储应降低费率，因为关税会加热</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/trump-says-fed-should-cut-rates-as-tariff-push-heats-up</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统说，美联储应降低利率，并随着官员的关税推动而权衡的经济成本而与美国中央银行分裂。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/trump-says-fed-should-cut-rates-as-tariff-push-heats-up</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Mar 2025 02:20:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普着手签署行政命令拆除教育部门</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/trump-set-to-sign-executive-order-eliminating-education-department</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）有望签署一项行政诉讼，要求官员采取措施在很大程度上拆除教育部，这是他为减少联邦政府及其劳动力规模的最新努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/trump-set-to-sign-executive-order-eliminating-education-department</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Mar 2025 22:48:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
